What you need to know:  Kenya, who have been improving gradually since their opening clash of the championships with Turkey, showed their bravery and hunger for a first win in the global championships, when they took the game to Argentina’s half from the startChampions Denmark and hosts Brazil are the other teams taking part in the women’s handballCoach Mwathi, who hailed goalkeeper Lilian Aisha for her brilliant display in the Games said the win over Argentina has motivated them to go for a third place finish